In Ek Date Aisi Bhi, join three friends as they set out on what they think will be the perfect romantic dates‚Ä¶ only for everything to go hilariously wrong! üò¨üíî
From awkward silences and weird restaurant choices to unexpected ex-encounters and disastrous conversations, each date turns into a comedy of errors. But just when all hope seems lost, a surprising twist brings unexpected connections and a dash of real love into the mix.
Full of laughs, relatable moments, and a sweet message, this sketch proves that sometimes, even the worst dates can lead to the best stories.‚ù§Ô∏è
#EkDateAisiBhi #ComedySketch #DateGoneWrong

Dhyan Sreenivasan Crashes Annie‚Äôs Kitchen! üòÇüçç Vishu Special with a Sweet Twist!

This Vishu, Annie's Kitchen is filled with laughter, surprises, and sweet moments as the charming Dhyan Sreenivasan joins Annie for a festive feast! üéâ

Annie starts off the celebration by preparing a special Vishu Pradhaman, a rich and delicious payasam that sets the mood just right. But the real surprise? Dhyan walks in as a guest and stuns Annie with his unexpected visit! üò≤üíõ

As Annie plans to treat Dhyan with a grand Vishu Sadya, she suddenly realizes she forgot to make kichadi ‚Äì specifically the pineapple version she had in mind. That‚Äôs when Dhyan steps in with full spirit, offering to help her in the kitchen! üççüë®‚Äçüç≥

Get ready for a cooking session packed with witty puns, playful banter, and heartwarming conversations as Annie and Dhyan team up to whip up the perfect Pineapple Kichadi. Along the way, Dhyan opens up about his latest projects, personal updates, and of course, adds his signature humor to every moment.

Don‚Äôt miss this fun-filled, flavor-packed Vishu Special Episode of Annie‚Äôs Kitchen! üåº‚ú®

snippet.title: Superman | Sneak Peek
snippet.description:
Krypto, take us home. #Superman - Only in Theaters July 11

‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who‚Äôs driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (‚ÄúTwisters,‚Äù ‚ÄúHollywood‚Äù) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (‚ÄúThe Marvelous Mrs. Maisel‚Äù) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the ‚ÄúX-Men‚Äù movies, ‚ÄúJuror #2‚Äù) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (‚ÄúFor All Mankind‚Äù), Anthony Carrigan (‚ÄúBarry,‚Äù ‚ÄúGotham‚Äù), Nathan Fillion (the ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), Isabela Merced (‚ÄúAlien Romulus‚Äù), Skyler Gisondo (‚ÄúLicorice Pizza,‚Äù ‚ÄúBooksmart‚Äù), Sara Sampaio (‚ÄúAt Midnight‚Äù), Mar√≠a Gabriela de Far√≠a (‚ÄúThe Moodys‚Äù), Wendell Pierce (‚ÄúSelma,‚Äù ‚ÄúTom Clancy‚Äôs Jack Ryan‚Äù), Alan Tudyk (‚ÄúAndor‚Äù), Pruitt Taylor Vince (‚ÄúBird Box‚Äù) and Neva Howell (‚ÄúGreedy People‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with editors William Hoy (‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù), Jason Ballantine (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù) and Craig Alpert (‚ÄúDeadpool 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlue Beetle‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù will be in theaters and IMAX nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

Welcome to Arranged Marriage, a heartfelt YouTube series that explores love found in the most unexpected way‚Äîthrough an arranged marriage! Follow the journey of two individuals brought together by family, tradition, and culture, who slowly discover friendship, trust, and eventually, love. Watch how their worlds collide and connect as they navigate new experiences, overcome misunderstandings, and learn what it means to truly love and respect each other.

Welcome back to Arranged Marriage Season 2! üéâ In Episode 1, the much-awaited first night takes an unexpected turn when Janani, the newly wedded wife, gets her period at the most awkward moment. üò≥ Ram, her modern-gen husband, steps up and handles the situation with care, love, and understanding. From midnight medical shop runs to comforting moments, this episode beautifully explores how real love blossoms in unexpected situations. ‚ù§Ô∏è

snippet.title: FilterCopy | Reality of a NEET Aspirant | Ft. Tanya Sharma, Ruma Mondal
snippet.description:
Being a NEET aspirant in India? It‚Äôs not just about books and mock tests‚Äîit's a whole emotional rollercoaster filled with anxiety, last-minute revision, relatives asking the wrong questions, and friends who mean well but say the weirdest things. üò©üìö

In this hilarious and painfully relatable FilterCopy sketch, we dive into the reality of a NEET student‚Äôs life‚Äîthe pressure, the panic, and of course, the people who keep saying things like:
üëâ ‚ÄúBeta, NEET nikaalna toh easy hai na?‚Äù
üëâ ‚ÄúArey Sharma ji ka beta bhi kar raha hai!‚Äù
üëâ ‚ÄúTumhe toh doctor banne ka passion hai na?‚Äù üòê

From group studies that turn into therapy sessions to panic before results day, this one‚Äôs for all the NEET warriors out there fighting their way through syllabus, stress, and society. üò≠‚úä

üéØ Tag a NEET aspirant who needs a laugh break!

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Episode 4346: Gokuldham Ki Holi
--------------------------------------------------------
Gokuldham Society comes together to celebrate Holika Dahan with great fervor, followed by lively Holi celebrations.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - promotes 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), a Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Title: Durga Chalisa

Lyrics:
Namo Namo Durge Sukh Karni
Namo Namo Ambe Dukh Harni
Nirakar Hai Jyoti Tumhari
Tihun Lok Phaili Ujiyari

Shashi Lalaat Mukh Maha Vishala
Netra Lal Bhrikouti Vikarala
Roop Maatu Ko Adhik Suhave
Darsh Karat Jan Ati Sukh Paave
Tum Sansar Shakti Ley Keena
Palan Hetu Anna Dhan Deena
Annapoorna Hui Jag Paala
Tumhi Aadi Sundari Bala

Pralayakal Sab Nashaan Haari
Tum Gouri Shiv Shankar Pyari
Shiv Yogi Tumhare Gun Gaavein
Brahma Vishnu Tumhein Nit Dhyaave
Roop Saraswati Ko Tum Dhara
De Subuddhi Rishi Munina Ubara
Dhara Roop Narsimha Ko Amba
Pragat Bhayi Phaad Kar Khamba

Raksha Kari Prahlad Bachayo
Hiranyaykush Ko Swarg Pathayo
Lakshmi Roop Dharo Jag Mahin
Shree Narayan Anga Samahin

Ksheer Sindhu Mein Karat Vilaasa
Daya Sindhu Deejey Mann Aasa
Hingalaja Mein Tumhi Bhawani
Mahima Amit Na Jaat Bakhani

Matangi Dhoomawati Mata
Bhuvaneshwari Bagala Sukhdata
Shree Bhairav Tara Jag Tarini
Chhinna Bhala Bhava Dukh Nivarini
Kehari Vahan Sohe Bhawani
Laangur Veer Chalat Agavani
Kar Mein Khappar Khadaga Virajay
Jako Dekh Kaal Darr Bhajey

Sohe Astra Aur Trishula
Jate Uthata Shatru Hiya Shoola

Nagkoti Mein Toumhi Virajat
Tihoun Lok Mein Danka Baajat
Shumbh Nishumbh Daanav Tum Maare
Rakta Beej Shankhana Sanghaare
Mahishasur Nrip Ati Abhimani
Jehi Agh Bhar Mahi Akulaani

Roop Karaal Kali Ka Dhara
Sena Sahita Tum Tihin Samhara
Pidh Pari Santana Par Jab Jab
Bhayi Sahay Maat Tum Tab Tab
Amarpuri Auro Sab Lokaa
Tab Mahima Sab Rahey Ashoka
Jwala Mein Hai Jyoti Tumhari
Tumhein Sada Poojey Nar Nari

Prem Bhakti Se Jo Jas Gaave
Dukh Daridra Nikat Nahin Aave
Dhyave Jo Nar Man Layi
Janma Maran Tako Chhouti Jaayi
Jogi Sur Muni Kahat Pukaari
Yog Nahi Bina Shakti Tumhari
Shankar Acharaj Tap Kinho
Kaamaru Krodh Jeet Sab Leenho

Nishdin Dhyan Dharo Shankar Ko
Kaahu Kaal Nahin Sumiro Tumko
Shakti Roop Ko Maram Na Paayo
Shakti Gayi Tab Mann Pachitayo
Sharnagat Huyi Kiriti Bakhai
Jai Jai Jai Jagadambe Bhawani

Bhayi Prasanna Aadi Jagadamba
Dayi Shakti Nahin Keen Vilamba

Maukon Maatu Kashta Ati Ghero
Tum Bin Kaun Hare Dukh Mero
Asha Trishna Nipat Satave
Ripu Murakh Mohi Ati Darpave
Shatru Nash Keejai Maharani
Soumiron Ikchit Tumhein Bhawani
Karo Kripa Hey Maatu Dayala
Riddhi Siddhi Dey Karahou Nihaala

Jab Lagi Jiyoun Daya Phal Paun
Tumharo Jas Mein Sada Sunaun
Durga Chalisa Jo Koi Gaavey
Sab Sukh Bhog Parampad Paave

Devidas Sharan Neej Jaani
Karahun Krupa Jagadambe Bhawani
Karahun Krupa Jagadambe Bhawani

Sharanagat Raksha Kare
Bhakt Rahe Nishank
Me Aaya Teri Sharan Mein

In this 482nd episode of The Ranveer Show, we welcome our TRS All Star - Rajarshi Nandy, for an insightful discussion on rebirth, spirituality, and life's challenges. Rajarshi shares his personal experiences and ancient wisdom to help us understand the deeper meaning behind life's difficulties, the importance of faith and devotion, and how spiritual practices can transform our lives.

This episode is perfect for anyone looking to deepen their spiritual journey and seeking practical guidance to navigate life's inevitable struggles.

(02:47) -  Spiritual Growth Through Suffering
(05:02) - Universal Nature of Suffering
(06:01) - Sri Aurobindo's Transformation
(09:09) - The Importance of Apology to the Deity
(10:20) - Fame, Jealousy & Protection
(15:26) - Building Spiritual Infrastructure
(20:01) - Life as a Spiritual Battlefield
(24:01) - Final Lessons
(26:20) - End of the podcast

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Jetha Aur Bhide Ki Nok Jhonk' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTAUo34hpXVbh1keqAyhuhj

Featured by actor Rani Panda & Arjun. Show all your love and support. Do watch and enjoy the video and definitely like, share and subscribe for more updates. Stay tuned and connected with us .
